{"tid":238770,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"自來雀","createTime":"2017-05-11T08:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T08:46:25.000Z","uid":99039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc5433f5abf186e0d3c1591f24dd1800ae234d5a","tid":238770,"uid":99039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T08:36:28.000Z","msg":"啱啱聽到個廳傳嚟pang pang聲<br />\n即刻出房睇<br />\n點知見到有隻雀仔(黑色細隻)<br />\n係咁撞向個窗(冷氣機隔離)<br />\n撞到好大力<br />\n因為下面先係正窗(開咗嘅)<br />\n我嗰刻覺得隻雀係想叫我<br />\n多過想飛入間屋<br />\n因為我住高層<br />\n住咗十幾年都未試過咁嘅情況<br />\n係咪有咩寓意<br />\n定我諗多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e913739e14b644f2eb34f48d5b35d323fa4e47","tid":238770,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T08:40:17.000Z","msg":"rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97791a0616489f16d06933b5d0c82aecac608a5","tid":238770,"uid":94438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T08:46:25.000Z","msg":"可以辦定身後事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}